    <h2>Sneaky Teacher</h2>
      
    <div class="content">
      <p>Welcome to the Sneaky Teacher App! This application is designed to provide a database of  activies for your Reluctant Learners. A Reluctant Learner is one who "is not interested in life at all, is not interested in what you are teaching, and is not able to learn in the time-frame or manner of presentation" according to Joyce Herzog (2002). This app will server a purpose of providing a database for lessons that promotes learning through phyical and kinetic activities.
      </p>

